We carried out a cost-effectiveness evaluation of transdermal fentanyl compared 
to three other widely used opioids: transdermal buprenorphine, sustained-release 
morphine, and controlled-release oxycodone from a third-party-payers 
perspective. A decision analytic model with data from a structured database 
